explanations.description: The tokens in this dataset appear to be words that are part of a phrase or sentence that has been extracted from a text, often in a discussion or translation of Islamic texts, and are often words that have specific meaning or are used in a particular context, such as prepositions ("of", "to", "in", etc.), words that introduce a quote or a statement ("that", "so", etc.), or words that are part of a title or name (e.g. "Hazrat", "Prophet", etc.).
